Package info.kgeorgiy.ja.koloskov.implementor

package info.kgeorgiy.ja.koloskov.implementor
The info.kgeorgiy.ja.koloskov.implementor package contains the implementation of the Implementor class, which generates implementations of interfaces and abstract classes, as well as creates JAR files containing these implementations.

Main classes in the package:

  • Implementor is the main class implementing the JarImpler interface, providing code generation functionality.
  • ClassImplementor is a helper class for generating implementation code.
  • ExecutableWrapper is an abstract wrapper class for methods and constructors.
  • ImplerException is an exception thrown when errors occur during code generation.

This package is part of a programming assignment in the "Java Advanced" course.
